<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als vns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / von
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Spılers des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_95_r1l24"><expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / vmb die arbeit cʒü Spalt / . Darvmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_95_r1l25"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir Jn cʒe rede geſacʒt
                        / . vnd er ſpricht / . Es hab ewr gnad mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_95_r1l26">Jm davon geredt vnd Jm <expan>gepot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        xvȷ .  <expan>lib<ex>rae</ex></expan>  . von der rüten / Aber es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_95_r1l28">ſeÿ <del rend="strikethrough">weder </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_95_line_1576565961108_404">nicht </ab></add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>leitkaufft</expan> noch habt Jm dheinen gots
                                <expan>pfenni<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darauf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_95_r1l29"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd der lon ſeÿ Jm
                        cʒeklein vnd müg daran nicht gehaben / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_95_r1l30">vnd <del rend="strikethrough">er getraw
                                    <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> wer ſein
                            <expan>verderb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſolt er den lon alſo nemen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_95_r1l31">vnd getraw <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol Jr begert ſeins
